- 18/05/2022
31. tls.c: ported for openssl 3.0.0
- 18/05/2022 - indimail-mta-3.0.0
- 30/05/2022
32. dotls.c: BUG \r not copied, extra \0 copied. Thanks Stefan Berger
33. dotls.c: Report line too long error instead of clubbing it with 'out of
